item.description: Works (under construction) For more information, go to bandcamp or soundcloud at the bottom of the site, or go to about. 2018/02/09 : Participated in “Shibuya-Kei Chiptune Cover Compilation” by OMOIDE LABEL x Bytedoll Records with “TWEEDEES - Baby, Baby (tobokegao Gameboy Cover) 2017/12/27 : Participated in 地獄でなぜサグい’s project “Gameboy Noise Jam 002 (Circuit Bent)” in the compilation “reversible chance operation”, which is a one-of-a-kind compilation with different sound effects as a result of randomly skipping oil on each CD
